@@ -25,6 +25,7 @@ This project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/).
 
 ### Changed
 
+* Change default value of `.editorconfig` property `ktlint_code_style` from `intellij_idea` to `ktlint_official`. The `ktlint_official` code style adheres to the best parts of the [Kotlin Coding Conventions](https://kotlinlang.org/docs/coding-conventions.html) and [Android Kotlin styleguide](https://developer.android.com/kotlin/style-guide), but is no longer restricted to produce code compatible with the default IntelliJ IDEA formatter which contains bugs that are still not resolved after multiple years.
 * Update dependency gradle to v8.2.1 ([#2122](https://github.com/pinterest/ktlint/pull/2122))
 * Update dependency org.codehaus.janino:janino to v3.1.10  ([#2110](https://github.com/pinterest/ktlint/pull/2110))
 * Update dependency com.google.jimfs:jimfs to v1.3.0 ([#2112](https://github.com/pinterest/ktlint/pull/2112))
